            "comment": "Goodsprings",
            "content": "Goodsprings is a small, quiet settlement in the Mojave Wasteland, built around a natural spring that gives the town its reliable water. It sits in the hills west of the I-15, near the old Nevada-California border. Its people are ranchers, prospectors, and settlers raising bighorners and brahmin and scraping by. The town has a general store, the Prospector Saloon, a schoolhouse, and a small cemetery on the hill. Keep Goodsprings grounded, dusty, and personal - most residents are ordinary folk, not adventurers, just people trying to hold onto their homes.",
