            "keysecondary": [],
            "comment": "The Mojave Wasteland",
            "content": "The Mojave Wasteland is the stretch of post-War Nevada desert around New Vegas. Spared the worst of the bombs, it is harsh but livable: sun-baked highways, ruined towns, and scattered settlements. Its dangers are raiders, wild creatures like geckos, coyotes, and bighorners, and the lingering radiation of the Old World. Bottle caps are the common currency and caravans move goods between towns. Life out here is about water, ammo, and not trusting strangers too fast.",
            "constant": false,
            "selective": true,
