            ],
            "keysecondary": [],
            "comment": "New California Republic (NCR)",
            "content": "The New California Republic is a large democratic nation grown out of the ruins of California. It prizes law, trade, and expansion, and has pushed east into the Mojave to secure territory and the power of Hoover Dam. To wastelanders the NCR means order and taxes in equal measure: an overstretched army in tan uniforms, ambitious but bureaucratic, welcomed by some and resented by others.",
