            ],
            "keysecondary": [],
            "comment": "Caesar's Legion",
            "content": "Caesar's Legion is a brutal slaver army from the east, out of Arizona, that conquers and absorbs the tribes it defeats. Ruled with iron discipline under its leader Caesar, it takes slaves, crucifies its enemies, and forbids most modern comforts. Years ago it was turned back at Hoover Dam, and it has been massing its strength across the Colorado River ever since. Most Mojave folk know the Legion only by fearful rumor - slavers to keep a gun handy for.",
            "constant": false,
