            "keysecondary": [],
            "comment": "New Vegas, the Strip & Mr. House",
            "content": "New Vegas is the walled casino city at the heart of the Mojave, spared destruction in the Great War. Its neon Strip is lined with casinos, while the poorer district of Freeside sprawls outside the walls. The city is quietly ruled by the reclusive Mr. House - Robert House, a pre-War RobCo genius who survived sealed inside the Lucky 38 tower - who keeps order through his army of robotic Securitrons. To most wastelanders, New Vegas is a distant place of lights, money, and machines.",
