            "keysecondary": [],
            "comment": "The Great War & the Old World",
            "content": "The Great War was the single day in 2077 when the old world ended: a nuclear exchange that scorched the earth in a few hours and buried pre-War America under fallout. The survivors crawled out of vaults and ruins to build a rougher world from the wreckage. People still dig up 'Old World' relics - technology, pre-War money, half-remembered brand names - as reminders of the life that was lost.",
